              <div className="p-3 bg-indigo-50 dark:bg-indigo-900/20 border border-indigo-100 dark:border-indigo-900/30 rounded-xl space-y-2">
                <h4 className="text-[10px] font-bold text-indigo-700 dark:text-indigo-400 uppercase tracking-tight">Troubleshooting Fetch Errors</h4>
                <div className="text-[10px] text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed space-y-1">
                  <p>1. Open <strong>LM Studio</strong> → Server tab.</p>
                  <p>2. Toggle <strong>Start Server</strong> ON.</p>
                  <p>3. Enable <strong>CORS</strong> (vital for web browser access).</p>
                  <p>4. Using mobile? Set URL to your computer's IP (e.g., <code>http://192.168.1.5:1234/v1</code>).</p>
                </div>
